channel.title: Ace of Spades Deuce
channel.description:
If you didn't know, Ace of Spades is a voxel-based FPS that was taken over by Jagex a little over a year ago. Looking at the [url=http://aceofspadeswiki.info/w/images/c/c3/DeuceBodyBlue.png]reference picture[/url], I modeled Deuce (which honestly isn't hard at all considering it's all just primitives). NO, this does not belong in the modeling section, because I didn't do this to show off any models I made, I did it solely for graphics.
The last one is really meant for a background, so it's probably best if you opened it in a new tab.
[img]http://fc03.deviantart.net/fs71/i/2013/294/5/6/ace_of_spades__deuce_by_travas2-d6rbpfa.png[/img] [img]http://fc02.deviantart.net/fs70/i/2013/294/9/5/ace_of_spades__deuce_by_travas2-d6rbpob.png[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/jVvR01z.jpg[/img]
[b][u]What do you guys think?[/u][/b]
